episodes.title: Episode 3: Let's Kick Some A**! 🚀
episodes.description: This week, we’re taking a sledgehammer to every network marketing myth you’ve been fed. Pyramid scheme? Cult? Get-rich-quick scam? We’re unpacking it all—no fluff, no sugarcoating, just straight facts. 🔥 What’s real, what’s a scam, and what’s actually worth your time? 💰 Is the network marketing industry even real, or are you missing out on the big money? 🎙️ We’re breaking it down, busting the myths, and giving you the real tea. Go listen to the latest episode now and let us know what you think—or drop your questions for a future deep dive! Follow @themilehighclubpod because we’re flying above the noise. ✈️💥 Follow Us: @themilehighclubpod
